Introduction

PEACH A! (피치아!), formerly known as PEACHDAY (피치데이) is a four member girl group under Better Company and KNJ Music. They were originally set to make their debut in October 14, 2021 with their first single “Cotton Candy”. They rebranded in May 17, 2022 as PEACH A!, and debuted on October 8, 2022 with their digital single "Rebreath"
